{"id":"api/core/NO_ERRORS_SCHEMA","title":"NO_ERRORS_SCHEMA","contents":"<article>\n  <div class=\"breadcrumb-container\">\n    <div class=\"breadcrumb\">\n      <script type=\"application/ld+json\">\n        {\n          \"@context\": \"http://schema.org\",\n          \"@type\": \"BreadcrumbList\",\n          \"itemListElement\": [\n            { \"@type\": \"ListItem\", \"position\": 1, \"item\": { \"@id\": \"https://angular.cn/api\", \"name\": \"API\" } },\n            { \"@type\": \"ListItem\", \"position\": 2, \"item\": { \"@id\": \"https://angular.cn/api/core\", \"name\": \"@angular/core\" } },\n            { \"@type\": \"ListItem\", \"position\": 3, \"item\": { \"@id\": \"https://angular.cn/api/core/NO_ERRORS_SCHEMA\", \"name\": \"NO_ERRORS_SCHEMA\" } }\n          ]\n        }\n      </script>\n        <a href=\"/api\">API</a> &gt; <a href=\"api/core\">@angular/core</a>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"github-links\">\n  <a href=\"https://github.com/ng-docs/angular-cn/edit/cn/packages/core/src/metadata/schema.ts?message=docs(core)%3A%20請簡述你的修改...#L63-L64\" aria-label=\"提供編輯建議\" title=\"提供編輯建議\"><i class=\"material-icons\" aria-hidden=\"true\" role=\"img\">mode_edit</i></a>\n  <a href=\"https://github.com/ng-docs/angular-cn/tree/16.1.0-next.3/packages/core/src/metadata/schema.ts#L63-L64\" aria-label=\"檢視原始碼\" title=\"檢視原始碼\"><i class=\"material-icons\" aria-hidden=\"true\" role=\"img\">code</i></a>\n</div>\n  </div>\n  <header ng-should-translate=\"\" class=\"api-header\">\n    <h1 id=\"no_errors_schema\">NO_ERRORS_SCHEMA<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"api/core/NO_ERRORS_SCHEMA#no_errors_schema\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h1>\n    <label class=\"api-type-label const\">const</label>\n  </header>\n  <aio-toc class=\"embedded\"></aio-toc>\n\n  <div class=\"api-body\">\n  <section ng-should-translate=\"\" class=\"short-description\">\n    <p translation-result=\"on\">定義一個架構，該架構允許任何元素上的任何屬性。</p><p translation-origin=\"off\">Defines a schema that allows any property on any element.</p>\n\n\n    <p no-translate=\"\"><a href=\"api/core/NO_ERRORS_SCHEMA#description\">檢視\"說明\"...</a></p>\n  </section>\n  <code-example language=\"ts\" hidecopy=\"true\" class=\"no-box api-heading\">\n  const <a href=\"api/core/NO_ERRORS_SCHEMA\" class=\"code-anchor\">NO_ERRORS_SCHEMA</a>: <a href=\"api/core/SchemaMetadata\" class=\"code-anchor\">SchemaMetadata</a>;\n  </code-example>\n\n  \n<section ng-should-translate=\"\" class=\"description\">\n  <h2 id=\"description\">說明<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"api/core/NO_ERRORS_SCHEMA#description\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h2>\n  <p translation-result=\"on\">此模式允許你忽略與範本中任何未知元素或屬性相關的錯誤。通常不鼓勵使用此模式，因為它會阻止有用的驗證，並且可能會在你的範本中隱藏真正的錯誤。考慮改用\n<code><a href=\"api/core/CUSTOM_ELEMENTS_SCHEMA\" class=\"code-anchor\">CUSTOM_ELEMENTS_SCHEMA</a></code>。</p><p translation-origin=\"off\">This schema allows you to ignore the errors related to any unknown elements or properties in a\ntemplate. The usage of this schema is generally discouraged because it prevents useful validation\nand may hide real errors in your template. Consider using the <code><a href=\"api/core/CUSTOM_ELEMENTS_SCHEMA\" class=\"code-anchor\">CUSTOM_ELEMENTS_SCHEMA</a></code> instead.</p>\n\n</section>\n</div>\n</article>\n\n<!-- links to this doc:\n - api/core\n - api/core/NgModule\n - api/core/SchemaMetadata\n - guide/testing-components-scenarios\n - guide/upgrade\n-->\n<!-- links from this doc:\n - /api\n - api/core\n - api/core/CUSTOM_ELEMENTS_SCHEMA\n - api/core/NO_ERRORS_SCHEMA#description\n - api/core/NO_ERRORS_SCHEMA#no_errors_schema\n - api/core/SchemaMetadata\n - https://github.com/ng-docs/angular-cn/edit/cn/packages/core/src/metadata/schema.ts?message=docs(core)%3A%20請簡述你的修改...#L63-L64\n - https://github.com/ng-docs/angular-cn/tree/16.1.0-next.3/packages/core/src/metadata/schema.ts#L63-L64\n-->"}